\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Sim. Tratamos de toda a documentação e assets necessários para aprovação nas stores. Tens de ter conta de developer (Apple Developer Program: $99/ano; Google Play: $25 único) — podemos orientar-te no processo de criação.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Posso adicionar funcionalidades após o lançamento?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Sim. O desenvolvimento é modular e documentado para que novas funcionalidades possam ser adicionadas facilmente. Oferecemos também contratos de manutenção mensal para updates contínuos.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"As vossas apps passam na revisão da Apple?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Sim. Conhecemos as diretrizes da App Store e desenvolvemos em conformidade. Nunca tivemos um projeto rejeitado definitivamente — casos de pedido de informação adicional foram resolvidos em menos de 48 horas.\\\"}}]}\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"12:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"svc-page\\\",\\\"data-color\\\":\\\"cyan\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L1c\\\",null,{\\\"color\\\":\\\"cyan\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L4\\\",null,{\\\"id\\\":\\\"ld-svc-apps-mobile\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"strategy\\\":\\\"afterInteractive\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"@context\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://schema.org\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Service\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"@id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://elementgroup.pt/servicos/apps-mobile#service\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Apps Mobile\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Desenvolvimento de apps mobile para iOS e Android em Portugal desde 1.497€. Apps nativas e PWA com painel de gestão incluído. Notificações push e integração com APIs.\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"url\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://elementgroup.pt/servicos/apps-mobile\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"provider\\\\\\\":{\\\